随着该游戏的高评价以及高销量，有关于本作的续作的消息开始出现。2012年10月，本作的制作人丹·索查接受英国版《PlayStation官方杂志》采访时表示希望本作可以成为一个游戏系列，但也表示此时他无法谈论是否确实有续作的消息，毕竟工作室的主要精力还集中在为《香港秘密警察》制作付费下载内容上。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2012/10/29/sleeping-dogs-has-6-months-dlc-planned-square-believed-in-this-game-as-a-potential-franchise/ |title=Sleeping Dogs producer says Square "believed in this game as a potential franchise", 6 months DLC planned |publisher=Official PlayStation Magazine |date=2012-10-29 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2012-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102181230/http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2012/10/29/sleeping-dogs-has-6-months-dlc-planned-square-believed-in-this-game-as-a-potential-franchise/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2013年10月，United Front Games正式宣布确定续作名称为《[[香港秘密警察：三合會之戰|香港秘密警察：三合會之戰]]》（Sleeping Dogs: Triad Wars），并继续交由[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯]]发行。<ref>[http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/86795.html 《香港秘密警察》續作有望？SQUARE ENIX 將推新作《三合會之戰》]</ref>2015年1月发布<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.unitedfrontgames.com/games/triad-wars/ |title= Triad Wars |author=  |website=  |publisher= United Front Games |language= en |accessdate= 2014-09-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140923142613/http://www.unitedfrontgames.com/games/triad-wars/ |archive-date= 2014-09-23 |dead-url= yes }}</ref> ，惟在2016年1月20日停止运营。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Futter|first1=Mike|title=Square Enix Shutting Down Free-To-Play Sleeping Dogs Success|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/12/23/square-enix-shutting-down-free-to-play-sleeping-dogs-successor-triad-wars.aspx|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|accessdate=23 December 2015|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225082159/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/12/23/square-enix-shutting-down-free-to-play-sleeping-dogs-successor-triad-wars.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 改编电影 ==
2017年3月，有报道称《香港秘密警察》将会改编成真人电影，由[[Original_Film|Original Film]]制作，并由著名影星[[甄子丹|甄子丹]]饰演沈威。<ref>[http://deadline.com/2017/03/donnie-yen-sleeping-dogs-neal-moritz-original-film-1201948700/ Donnie Yen To Headline ‘Sleeping Dogs’ For Neal Moritz’s Original Film] {{Wayback|url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/donnie-yen-sleeping-dogs-neal-moritz-original-film-1201948700/ |date=20180204212748 }}.Deadline.2017-03-02.[2017-03-03].</ref><ref>[http://www.polygon.com/2017/3/2/14797432/sleeping-dogs-movie-donnie-yen-original-film Sleeping Dogs movie in development with Donnie Yen].Polygon.2017-03-02.[2017-03-03].</ref> 2018年2月，甄子丹在個人Instagram上發布照片，證實此事。

